        jEditorPane1.setText("The Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning (AI/ML) Club is an organization at APSIT. It is a community of students who are enthusiastic and inspired\nabout the new fields of AI and ML. The AIML Club intends to serve as a meeting space for students interested in learning, debating, and applying AI/ML\nto all types of problem-solving, whether academic or practical.In recent times, with better and cheaper computational power, and a colossal amount\nof data generated every day, AI and ML are finding broader and deeper applications in every area. However, in APSIT, we lacked a dedicated club to\ncater to the large community of students interested in this field. AIML Club strives to address this void by being the one-stop destination for APSIT\nstudents passionate about AI/ML.\n");
        jScrollPane2.setViewportView(jEditorPane1);

